Mango Orange Julius⁠

Strawberry Mint⁠
⁠
2 oz. Blue Chair Bay® White Rum⁠
3 fresh strawberries, muddled⁠
8 fresh mint leaves⁠
1/2 lemon, juiced⁠
1 oz. simple syrup⁠
⁠
